* VCS tag to version converter
  A database table to hold regexp(?) to convert tags into valid version numbers (e.g. maven-3.0.4 -> 3.0.4)

* target path's for wars
  We already have a path on the server (server.targetdir), but we also need a path to store the wars relative to it

* EAR support
  Pretty much the same as wars

* JAR support
  Pretty much the same as wars

* Extraction support
  Extracting data from a given path in the JAR to a given directory
  Should this be attached below WAR/EAR/JAR or directly attached to project?

* Maven repository support
  Specify a list of repositories to download maven artifacts from
  configurable per project?